{"tid":817590,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[樓市GOGOGO] 全球最高危樓市報告！香港有份　未來5年下跌空間5成","createTime":"2018-09-13T12:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T04:27:40.000Z","uid":147097,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2bbc89fc2b6c4ed23b4e70bdeda17c5d0b4858c5","tid":817590,"uid":147097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:52:01.000Z","msg":"外國傳媒報道，英國經濟研究機構牛津經濟公司(Oxford Economics)發表最新報告，警告包括香港在內的樓市危險程度已到了「特別敏感」的階段，根據往績，這將對經濟活動構成威脅。其中，香港樓價超出長期平均值1.03倍，意味下跌空間達5成。<br />\n<br />\n該機構首席經濟師Adam Slater說：「(這些地區)在所有4個方面估值都非常高。它們的樓市升浪已很長、債務水平很高，而且浮動利率債務佔了重要比例(意味難以抵抗利率大幅上揚)。」<br />\n<br />\n報告顯示，目前全球樓市最高危的地區包括瑞典、澳洲、加拿大、香港、新西蘭、丹麥、挪威、英國、瑞士、南非。較大型經濟體情況則較正面，美國、德國、法國、中國、日本等，未見有明顯高危的徵狀。<br />\n<br />\nSlater指出，未來會導致高危地區樓價下跌的因素是「加息」。以澳洲為例，今年首8個月大型城市樓價已跌近3%，計及去年，為連跌11個月；其中，悉尼樓價已挫5.6%，原因是當地4大銀行之中，有3間已上調按揭利率。<br />\n<br />\n該機構指出，根據1970至2013年往績，樓價較長期平均值被高估35%或以上的地區，它們的實際樓價(即扣除通脹後)在未來5年將有75%時間下跌，即未來5年，有3.75年是跌市。換句話說，樓價再上升的空間很小，而且一旦下跌，將會顯著打擊經濟活動。由1997年起數據顯示，消費者開支與實際樓價變動是正關連。<br />\n<br />\n從本文附上的圖可見，瑞典、澳洲、加拿大、香港、新西蘭、挪威、英國的樓價均較長期平均值被高估35%或以上，據往績，未來5年可能有3.75年下跌，以香港樓價被高估1.03倍計，意味下跌空間達5成。"},{"pid":"b0c1cc6cfc0409c6b3b266b234109ee194399295","tid":817590,"uid":17103,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T12:54:50.000Z","msg":"香港樓市高危大陸無問題 ..<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/03/034503_9cc2f474881829c0cfa135397727b6a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F03%2F034503_9cc2f474881829c0cfa135397727b6a2.jpg&h=7445d352&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5905483b84cb00ea50548796ec417129f79406a3","tid":817590,"uid":171446,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:10:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37666501a962dfa3520e3002d74ca56fbe980c4e","tid":817590,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:33:04.000Z","msg":"樓爆 啪啪啪<br />\n樓爆 啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6a99f10cf942039e836f223e2122cc2c3890e5","tid":817590,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:49:49.000Z","msg":"林太<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732f512e82093ca714356674a13ea3c5414921f0","tid":817590,"uid":107590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"冇大陸份？"},{"pid":"f793c537d3e2062bb01be11117fd6b5e06f4bfc6","tid":817590,"uid":17866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"732f512e82093ca714356674a13ea3c5414921f0","tid":817590,"uid":107590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T13:53:55.000Z","msg":"冇大陸份？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-14T00:40:17.000Z","msg":"大陸唔比賣<br />\n唔比爆<br />\n因為要收房產稅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e11462817df777b5f927885a6bc49b10c730dfd","tid":817590,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T04:25:15.000Z","msg":"大陸樓價劈左五成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f27cc27274808c2c6de1dde0d7fb315b22a3ff","tid":817590,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T04:27:40.000Z","msg":"真係跌咪加到250囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}